    <h2 class="dek">The acclaimed author on hope, science, and writing about the future.</h2>
    
    <div class="byline" id="main_byline">
        By <a rel="author" href="http://www.slate.com/authors.ed_finn.html">Ed Finn</a>
    </div>
    

    





  
  
  


<div class="social horiz-counts-mobile centered sharing-buttons">
  
